column5: hey guys check out the weather for boxing day the news as well says we will get maybe 5-10 in the GTA,and areas north will get more in the usual snowbelt regions,but they say it will be short lived the temps will still be above normal and doesn"t look good for jan 1st opener check it out...oh and merry christmas,my liitle girl is so excited,she cant wait   cheers.  shawn

Should be an interesting weather day for sure!!!  It still may be mostly rain here, but not too far to the north, they are expecting snow!!  My little one wanted to make a snowman...and cant wait til it snows....Looks like I may have a one day window to help her with one!!!  Merry Christmas Shawn!!!  and everyone else too!!!
5-10 of snow, i guess I'll be hearing BRAP BRAP around my house woot
